      "HEADER": [
        "Home > Gamemastering > Bestiary > Outsiders > Tonberry Family > Baby Paleberry Table of Contents This small pale little guy wear dark blue cloaks with hoods and carry an newly-fashioned lantern and a small butcher knife. Baby Paleberry (CR 1/3)",
