        "Languages Tonberry; telepathy 30 ft. Gear Tiny butcher knife, lantern"
      ],
      "SPECIAL ABILITIES": [
        "Baby’s",
        "Grudge (Su) 1/day, as long as the baby paleberry is not making a knife attack, it may use its Baby's Grudge ability on a single target within 30 ft. The target takes 1d4 points of holy damage (Fortitude save DC 12 for half damage). Chef’s",
        "Knife (Ex) Once per round, a baby paleberry may make a melee attack with its knife. If a creature is struck by it, it must make a Fortitude save (DC 9) or takes the sickened status effect for 1 round. Those who are immune to critical hits are immune to this and take the knife damage only. The knife is only deadly in the hands of a baby paleberry, who has finesse training with it. Familiar The master of a baby paleberry gains a +3 bonus on Spellcraft checks to identify magic items"
      ]
